DefaultChoiceDisplayText.SourceString: I can work it out [Skip Tutorial]
DefaultChoiceDisplayText.LocalizedString: I can work it out [Skip Tutorial]

DefaultChoiceDisplayText.SourceString: Can you tell me about Ashenfall?
DefaultChoiceDisplayText.LocalizedString: Can you tell me about Ashenfall?

Message.SourceString: Welcome to Ashenfall, sorry about the mess. Had a bit of a dragon problem, that's why we've called for you.
Message.LocalizedString: Welcome to Ashenfall, sorry about the mess. Had a bit of a dragon problem, that's why we've called for you.

Message.SourceString: Oh dear, you just walked right past the Wise Old Man. He won't like that. Best go back and say hi, eh?
Message.LocalizedString: Oh dear, you just walked right past the Wise Old Man. He won't like that. Best go back and say hi, eh?

Message.SourceString: By Saradomin's big bushy beard! Just our luck, a great ruddy dragon. Think it were him that got the others - may they rest in peace.
Message.LocalizedString: By Saradomin's big bushy beard! Just our luck, a great ruddy dragon. Think it were him that got the others - may they rest in peace.

Message.SourceString: Now you've got something to fight with, go chat to Vannaka over to the north east, he can teach you how to keep fighting fit.
Message.LocalizedString: Now you've got something to fight with, go chat to Vannaka over to the north east, he can teach you how to keep fighting fit.

Message.SourceString: But look at you, all skin and bones. Must be proper parched after a journey like that.
Message.LocalizedString: But look at you, all skin and bones. Must be proper parched after a journey like that.

Message.SourceString: But not here. Come find me in Bramblemead Village, and we'll get you started.
Message.LocalizedString: But not here. Come find me in Bramblemead Village, and we'll get you started.

Message.SourceString: Still, it's going to be tough surviving this place with a dragon about.
Message.LocalizedString: Still, it's going to be tough surviving this place with a dragon about.

Message.SourceString: Zanik says boiling it sorts it all out. So might want to give that a look later, when you've got a chance. Anyway, time we got you all set up to survive this harsh land.
Message.LocalizedString: Zanik says boiling it sorts it all out. So might want to give that a look later, when you've got a chance. Anyway, time we got you all set up to survive this harsh land.

Message.SourceString: Me? Name's Doric. I'm just a stupid old blacksmith that got swept up in tales of adventure. Trying to win back me glory days.
Message.LocalizedString: Me? Name's Doric. I'm just a stupid old blacksmith that got swept up in tales of adventure. Trying to win back me glory days.

Message.SourceString: Ah, but you've got a good head on yer shoulders. I see you've already got some water, so you won't die of thirst.
Message.LocalizedString: Ah, but you've got a good head on yer shoulders. I see you've already got some water, so you won't die of thirst.

Message.SourceString: Dehydration and starvation are deadlier than dragons, so you're going to need keep an eye on your basic needs, like hunger and thirst.
Message.LocalizedString: Dehydration and starvation are deadlier than dragons, so you're going to need keep an eye on your basic needs, like hunger and thirst.

Message.SourceString: I've marked two ponds on your map, to the northwest and south of us. Grab some water from there and bring it back here. Then I'll teach you what you'll need to survive.
Message.LocalizedString: I've marked two ponds on your map, to the northwest and south of us. Grab some water from there and bring it back here. Then I'll teach you what you'll need to survive.

Message.SourceString: Oh dear, you seem a little overburdened at the moment. Come and see me when you've got some space free in your backpack.
Message.LocalizedString: Oh dear, you seem a little overburdened at the moment. Come and see me when you've got some space free in your backpack.

Message.SourceString: If you see a redberry bush along the way, grab yourself a handful. Not much of a meal, but a little food is better than no food at all.
Message.LocalizedString: If you see a redberry bush along the way, grab yourself a handful. Not much of a meal, but a little food is better than no food at all.

Message.SourceString: Left my son behind to watch the shop. Good lad, gonna do good things. Hope he's not too worried about his dad.
Message.LocalizedString: Left my son behind to watch the shop. Good lad, gonna do good things. Hope he's not too worried about his dad.

Message.SourceString: I've marked two ponds on your map, to the northwest and south of us. Grab some water from there and bring it back here. Then I'll teach you what you'll need to survive.
Message.LocalizedString: I've marked two ponds on your map, to the northwest and south of us. Grab some water from there and bring it back here. Then I'll teach you what you'll need to survive.

Message.SourceString: Still, no point lollygagging around. I'll catch my breath and then explore these new lands. Who knows? Might find something.
Message.LocalizedString: Still, no point lollygagging around. I'll catch my breath and then explore these new lands. Who knows? Might find something.

Message.SourceString: It's a wild place this. Beasties everywhere, and no civilisation in sight. Just the remnants, ghosts of the past.
Message.LocalizedString: It's a wild place this. Beasties everywhere, and no civilisation in sight. Just the remnants, ghosts of the past.

Message.SourceString: But you see that great tower, off in the distance? That's dragonkin that is. Means there's probably stuff worth finding about this place.
Message.LocalizedString: But you see that great tower, off in the distance? That's dragonkin that is. Means there's probably stuff worth finding about this place.

Message.SourceString: Ah, good, you've got some nice clean water there. The water in lakes and rivers tends to be dirty, tainted by something nasty that will make life difficult if you drink too much.
Message.LocalizedString: Ah, good, you've got some nice clean water there. The water in lakes and rivers tends to be dirty, tainted by something nasty that will make life difficult if you drink too much.

Message.SourceString: He's the only dwarf on the continent, that we know of anyway, can't miss him.
Message.LocalizedString: He's the only dwarf on the continent, that we know of anyway, can't miss him.

Message.SourceString: And look at ya! Not a knife to yer name, no, no, we can't be doing with that. Come on, let's get you prepared. You need to go and craft a stone club.
Message.LocalizedString: And look at ya! Not a knife to yer name, no, no, we can't be doing with that. Come on, let's get you prepared. You need to go and craft a stone club.

Message.SourceString: It won't kill a dragon, but it's better than nothing and it'll help you live a bit longer, giving you time to make something better.
Message.LocalizedString: It won't kill a dragon, but it's better than nothing and it'll help you live a bit longer, giving you time to make something better.

Message.SourceString: But before all that, how about we take you through some survival basics?
Message.LocalizedString: But before all that, how about we take you through some survival basics?

Message.SourceString: You'll want to get to grips with gathering and crafting first, Doric can help you with that.
Message.LocalizedString: You'll want to get to grips with gathering and crafting first, Doric can help you with that.

Message.SourceString: You'll need to gather stone and ash logs, which you can find laying around, then you'll want to build a crafting table to craft the club.
Message.LocalizedString: You'll need to gather stone and ash logs, which you can find laying around, then you'll want to build a crafting table to craft the club.

Message.SourceString: You'll find him outside the temple. Check your map if you get lost, but he should be easy to spot.
Message.LocalizedString: You'll find him outside the temple. Check your map if you get lost, but he should be easy to spot.

Message.SourceString: Oh, I'm Doric by the way. Resident blacksmith and craftsperson on this expedition. Nice to meet you. Now, stop standing around and go make that club!
Message.LocalizedString: Oh, I'm Doric by the way. Resident blacksmith and craftsperson on this expedition. Nice to meet you. Now, stop standing around and go make that club!

Message.SourceString: You've come at a great time. Heroic opportunities await. This long-forgotten place is just screaming to be explored.
Message.LocalizedString: You've come at a great time. Heroic opportunities await. This long-forgotten place is just screaming to be explored.

Message.SourceString: Ah good, you've got some water. Bit dirty, I know, but better than nothing. Be careful though, the water's tainted and it'll make life difficult if you drink too much.
Message.LocalizedString: Ah good, you've got some water. Bit dirty, I know, but better than nothing. Be careful though, the water's tainted and it'll make life difficult if you drink too much.

Message.SourceString: And look at ya! Not a knife to yer name, no, no, we can't be doing with that. Come on, let's get you prepared. You need to go and craft a stone club.
Message.LocalizedString: And look at ya! Not a knife to yer name, no, no, we can't be doing with that. Come on, let's get you prepared. You need to go and craft a stone club.

Message.SourceString: Oh, I'm Doric by the way. Resident blacksmith and craftsperson on this expedition. Nice to meet you. Now, stop standing around and go make that club!
Message.LocalizedString: Oh, I'm Doric by the way. Resident blacksmith and craftsperson on this expedition. Nice to meet you. Now, stop standing around and go make that club!

Message.SourceString: It won't kill a dragon, but it's better than nothing and it'll help you live a bit longer, giving you time to make something better.
Message.LocalizedString: It won't kill a dragon, but it's better than nothing and it'll help you live a bit longer, giving you time to make something better.

Message.SourceString: You'll need to gather stone and ash logs, which you can find laying around, then you'll want to build a crafting table to craft the club.
Message.LocalizedString: You'll need to gather stone and ash logs, which you can find laying around, then you'll want to build a crafting table to craft the club.

Message.SourceString: Now, even the best weapons break over time. When that happens use a crafting bench to repair your gear.
Message.LocalizedString: Now, even the best weapons break over time. When that happens use a crafting bench to repair your gear.

Message.SourceString: Before you go, here, something to help you on your way.
Message.LocalizedString: Before you go, here, something to help you on your way.

Message.SourceString: Oh, you made a dagger, not a club? Aye, it's a nice piece of work, not what I asked for, but that's fine.
Message.LocalizedString: Oh, you made a dagger, not a club? Aye, it's a nice piece of work, not what I asked for, but that's fine.

Message.SourceString: Gathering resources and crafting items, that's the basics of survival in this place. Seek out new resources to discover new recipes.
Message.LocalizedString: Gathering resources and crafting items, that's the basics of survival in this place. Seek out new resources to discover new recipes.

Message.SourceString: You'll want to build yourself a crafting table. Then once you've done that craft yourself a stone club.
Message.LocalizedString: You'll want to build yourself a crafting table. Then once you've done that craft yourself a stone club.

Message.SourceString: Strange place this. Ashenfall, I mean. Could make a real home here, if things stopped trying to kill us.
Message.LocalizedString: Strange place this. Ashenfall, I mean. Could make a real home here, if things stopped trying to kill us.

Message.SourceString: Aye, that's a fine club you got there, but even the best weapons break over time. When that happens use a crafting bench to repair your gear.
Message.LocalizedString: Aye, that's a fine club you got there, but even the best weapons break over time. When that happens use a crafting bench to repair your gear.

Message.SourceString: Both require stone and ash logs, which you'll find scattered all over the ground around here.
Message.LocalizedString: Both require stone and ash logs, which you'll find scattered all over the ground around here.

Message.SourceString: Fair enough, I do like someone that can show initiative.
Message.LocalizedString: Fair enough, I do like someone that can show initiative.
